parameters: Kru: "Ouch, ouch. Ah! That thing just now..."

Kru: "Sorry, I didn't expect someone to be running in the mountains like
this."
Umi: "Hmph... Ah! That thing just now! You... I hate you!"
Umi: "Umi... hates pain... You caused Umi pain. That's why I hate you."

Kru: "I know I did something bad, but I don't think you have to say it like
that. You ran into me too!"
Umi: "Umi is in a hurry. So it's okay."

Kru: "I'm in a hurry too! I have to save a cat! I'm more rushed than you
are!"
Kru: "Eh?! What?! Why are you so angry?!"

Kru: "Ah, yeah... A cat was being attacked by a monster... I was chasing
after it."
Umi: "Which way did it go! Take me with you!"
Kru: "Ah, this is just a scratch."
